title: Copy Project dialog UI issues in Navigator
description: When trying to copy a project in the Navigator, I encountered some UI problems, and the text displaying the bug number is in red.
OB: Upon choosing the project name as 'test,' a static text validation error message is displayed on the dialog in red.
EB: I expect that when selecting the project name 'test,' no validation error message should appear. The Copy Project dialog UI should function smoothly without any visual glitches or error messages.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Open the Navigator.
2. Attempt to copy a project.
3. In the dialog that appears, set the project name to 'test.'
